caption: Happy birthday Jack!! You and Johnson literally are my reason to smile. Every day I wake up to one of your songs as my alarm and I listen to your music while getting ready. When you guys tweet I get excited to hear about your life. And when you snapchat I'm happy to see what you're doing. I know there is a slim chance of you even seeing this but anyways happy birthday and thank you for making me happy; I love you soooooo much!! Keep being you because you're all that matters to me <3
